      <title>近一半的英国税务人员未能达到在办公室工作的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/almost-half-of-uk-tax-collectors-miss-target-to-work-in-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国政府高级官员称，近一半的英国税务人员未能满足政府部门要求员工每周三天在办公室工作的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/almost-half-of-uk-tax-collectors-miss-target-to-work-in-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派领袖表示他愿意与马杜罗会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/venezuelan-opposition-leader-says-he-d-be-open-to-talks-with-maduro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派候选人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯表示，如果他赢得今年的选举，他将愿意与总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗进行会谈，以确保权力的顺利移交。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/venezuelan-opposition-leader-says-he-d-be-open-to-talks-with-maduro</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:07:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯国防部长绍伊古因关键盟友被捕而削弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russian-defense-minister-shoigu-weakened-by-arrest-of-key-ally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，俄罗斯国防部长谢尔盖·绍伊古最亲密的盟友之一因涉嫌受贿被捕，削弱了他在总统弗拉基米尔·普京可能进行政府改组之前的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russian-defense-minister-shoigu-weakened-by-arrest-of-key-ally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克和肖尔茨找到了在防守上互相支持的共同目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/rishi-sunak-olaf-scholz-find-common-cause-to-support-each-other-on-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在上个月，英国与德国的关系似乎陷入紧张，英国官员游说柏林向乌克兰派遣更多远程导弹。周三，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 接待了里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak)，这是他作为总理首次访问德国，但几乎没有迹象表明存在如此紧张的局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/rishi-sunak-olaf-scholz-find-common-cause-to-support-each-other-on-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求佐治亚州法官撤销选举案中的两项罪名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/trump-asks-georgia-judge-to-toss-two-counts-in-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普要求法官撤销佐治亚州选举舞弊案中的两项罪名，称当地富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯不能指控他在联邦法院提交虚假文件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/trump-asks-georgia-judge-to-toss-two-counts-in-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:20:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 称法律站在一边，准备对抗美国禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/tiktok-says-law-is-on-its-side-as-it-prepares-to-fight-us-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok表示，美国国会周二晚间通过的立法将迫使其中国母公司出售其股份，否则该应用程序将在美国面临全面禁令，该立法“违宪”，该公司将在法庭上提出质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/tiktok-says-law-is-on-its-side-as-it-prepares-to-fight-us-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:19:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登签署援助法案，命令乌克兰援助在数小时内到位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-signs-aid-bill-says-help-headed-to-ukraine-within-hours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登签署了一项价值 950 亿美元的国家安全一揽子计划，并表示将在“数小时内”开始向乌克兰提供援助，结束了与共和党就长期拖延的对基辅和其他被围困的美国盟友的援助而展开的激烈斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-signs-aid-bill-says-help-headed-to-ukraine-within-hours</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:09:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强对黎巴嫩真主党的跨境打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/israel-said-it-struck-around-40-hezbollah-sites-in-south-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方表示，袭击了黎巴嫩南部约 40 个与真主党有关的地点，这显然是自加沙战争爆发以来双方几乎每天都发生的小冲突的升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/israel-said-it-struck-around-40-hezbollah-sites-in-south-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 12:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其的“正统”支点使里拉成为汇丰银行的最爱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-s-orthodox-pivot-makes-lira-a-favorite-for-hsbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其回归更传统的货币政策方式正在提振投资者信心，为资本流入奠定基础，并支撑汇丰控股有限公司对该国资产的看涨立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-s-orthodox-pivot-makes-lira-a-favorite-for-hsbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 10:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登签署援助计划并将伊朗石油制裁纳入法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/senate-sends-aid-package-with-iran-oil-sanctions-to-biden-s-desk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，总统乔·拜登签署了一项对外援助计划，其中将对伊朗石油行业的制裁纳入法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/senate-sends-aid-package-with-iran-oil-sanctions-to-biden-s-desk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:55:02 GMT</pubDate>
